about.summary: A Chinese Calendar Library in Pure Python

name: lunardate
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "lunardate" %}
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6c9c96d9f01522a10ab35df1a9b48707ae64a086f13fd34498b43f465918cc6f

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - lunardate

about:
  home: https://github.com/lidaobing/python-lunardate
  license: GPL-3.0
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'A Chinese Calendar Library in Pure Python'


extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bletham
